OL,3,CRicky Hatton's family pay tribute to
OL,4,Cboxer who had 'heart as big as his
OL,5,Csmile'
OL,7,FThe family of boxer Ricky Hatton say
OL,8,Fit has been a "great source of comfort
OL,9,Fto see just how many lives he touched"
OL,10,Fas they paid tribute to the dad and
OL,11,Fgranddad who had a "heart as big as
OL,12,Fhis smile".
OL,14,FThe 46-year-old boxing legend died on
OL,15,FSunday 14 September after Greater
OL,16,FManchester Police discovered his body
OL,17,Fat his home in Hyde. There are no
OL,18,Fsuspicious circumstances.
