OL,3,CRicky Hatton's family pay tribute to
OL,4,Cboxer who had 'heart as big as his
OL,5,Csmile'
OL,7,FIn a statement, issued by police, his
OL,8,Ffamily said: "It is with the heaviest
OL,9,Fof hearts that we announce the passing
OL,10,Fof our beloved son Richard.
OL,12,F"Richard was so much more than a world
OL,13,Fchampion. To us he was simply
OL,14,F'Richard', our son. A loving father,
OL,15,Fgrandfather, and brother, and a true
OL,16,Ffriend to many.
OL,18,F"He had a heart as big as his smile,
OL,19,Fand his kindness, humour and loyalty
OL,20,Ftouched everyone who was lucky enough
OL,21,Fto know him."
