OL,7,FHatton's death came after the world
OL,8,Fchampion boxer announced his return to
OL,9,Fboxing with a fight planned in
OL,10,FDecember.
OL,12,FPaying tribute to his sporting talent
OL,13,Fhis family said he "never forgot where
OL,14,Fhe came from".
OL,16,F"To the wider world, Richard will
OL,17,Falways be remembered as one of
OL,18,Fboxing's greatest champions - a man
OL,19,Fwho gave everything inside the ring
OL,20,Fand wore his heart on his sleeve
OL,21,Foutside of it," his family continued.
