OL,3,CRicky Hatton's family pay tribute to
OL,4,Cboxer who had 'heart as big as his
OL,5,Csmile'
OL,7,F"He inspired generations with his
OL,8,Ffighting spirit, his humility, and his
OL,9,Flove for the sport.
OL,11,F"But beyond the titles, the nights to
OL,12,Fremember, and the roar of the crowd,
OL,13,Fhe remained the same down-to-earth
OL,14,FRichard who never forgot where he came
OL,15,Ffrom."
