OL,3,CRicky Hatton's family pay tribute to
OL,4,Cboxer who had 'heart as big as his
OL,5,Csmile'
OL,7,FAs a family, our loss is immeasurable,
OL,8,Fand words cannot truly capture the
OL,9,Fpain we feel. Yet in the midst of our
OL,10,Fgrief, we have been deeply moved by
OL,11,Fthe overwhelming outpouring of love
OL,12,Fand support.
OL,14,F"It has been a source of great comfort
OL,15,Fto see just how many lives Richard
OL,16,Ftouched, and how widely he was admired
OL,17,Fand respected.
