OL,3,CRicky Hatton's family pay tribute to
OL,4,Cboxer who had 'heart as big as his
OL,5,Csmile'
OL,7,F"At this time, we kindly ask for
OL,8,Fprivacy as we come to terms with life
OL,9,Fwithout him. In the days and weeks
OL,10,Fahead, we will take strength from one
OL,11,Fanother and from the knowledge that
OL,12,FRichard's legacy - both in boxing and
OL,13,Fas a man - will continue to live on.
OL,15,F"Richard's memory will forever remain
OL,16,Fin our hearts, in the hearts of his
OL,17,Ffans, and in the sport he loved so
OL,18,Fdearly."
